<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM4.2.5">
<l>oruvā raṇampaṇi koṇṭavaṉ poykaiyil kañcaṉtaṉ</l>
<l>oruvā raṇamuyi ruṇṭavaṉ ceṉṟuṟai yummalai</l>
<l>karuvā raṇantaṉ piṭituṟan tōṭa kaṭalvaṇṇaṉ</l>
<l>tiruvā ṇaikūṟat tiriyuntaṇ māliruñ cōlaiyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The mountain where comes and dwells</l>
<l rend="indent">the one who took in service one elephant in a pond</l>
<l rend="indent">[and] consumed the life of Kaṃsa’s elephant,</l>
<l>is cool Tirumāliruñcōlai where wanders a dark elephant,</l>
<l rend="indent">foresaking its mate when it fled</l>
<l rend="indent">in order to utter a holy vow to the sea-hued One.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
